    <div id="comment_46498565">
        <header data-points="2" data-reason="Funny">
            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:Sounds Wonderful"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:Sounds Wonderful<span> (2, Funny)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~tomhath" class="author" title="author name and user ID">tomhath (637240) </a> | about 4 months ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4904573&cid=46498565">(#46498565)</a></h4>
