            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:Sounds Wonderful"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:Sounds Wonderful<span> (2)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~Greyfox" class="author" title="author name and user ID">Greyfox (87712) </a> | about 4 months ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4904573&cid=46498937">(#46498937)</a></h4>
